flowchart TD
    A[Turn completes] --> B{Remaining space<br/>below 13K?}
    B -->|No| C[Continue normally]
    B -->|Yes| D[Reserve 20K for summary]
    D --> E[Fire pre-compact hooks]
    E --> F[Model generates summary]
    F --> G[Replace older messages<br/>with boundary marker]
    G --> H[Turn resumes]
